des: Having trouble deciding what you need to start doing, stop doing, or what to invent for the New Year, or any time you like? Just want a quick laugh? Give me My Resolutions and get one of millions of different possible earnest and heartfelt resolutions. One will surely improve your life, or maybe just your day.
